OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FA Harvard astronomer known for
OL,7,Fcontroversial theories about alien
OL,8,Fvisits has been appointed by the White
OL,9,FHouse to lead a team of scientists to
OL,10,Fstudy the national security risks
OL,11,Fposed by UFOs.
OL,13,FAvi Loeb, a cosmologist who studied
OL,14,Fblack holes and served as the head of
OL,15,FHarvard's astronomy department until
OL,16,F2020, was chosen to lead a new
OL,17,Fscientific advisory council tasked
OL,18,Fwith investigating the origins of
OL,19,Fmysterious orbs and other objects
OL,20,Freported by military personnel in
OL,21,Frecent years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FIt is part of President Donald Trump's
OL,7,Fpush to provide more transparency on
OL,8,Fquestions on UFOs and alien life.
OL,10,FSo far, the Pentagon has released
OL,11,Fthree batches of files ranging from
OL,12,Fdecades-old FBI reports to more recent
OL,13,Fmilitary videos showing orbs darting
OL,14,For soaring through the sky.
OL,16,FLoeb's team will report to a new White
OL,17,FHouse panel focused on UFOs, now often
OL,18,Freferred to as unidentified anomalous
OL,19,Fphenomena, or UAP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,F"It's like a detective story," Loeb
OL,7,Fsaid in an interview. "It's a lot of
OL,8,Ffun, as long as you don't pay too much
OL,9,Fattention to the critics."
OL,11,FFor the last decade, Loeb has been
OL,12,Fscanning the skies and seas for
OL,13,Fevidence of intelligent alien life.
OL,15,FHe started in 2017, as scientists
OL,16,Fpuzzled over an interstellar object
OL,17,Fsoaring by Earth. While others
OL,18,Fproposed it was a comet or ice chunk,
OL,19,FLoeb said it could be a thin "light
OL,20,Fsail" detached from an alien
OL,21,Fspacecraft.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@^O]oD@WOUqD@ZO]{D@^OU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
