FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FHis theories have won praise in UFO
OL,7,Fcircles but often put him in conflict
OL,8,Fwith academic peers.
OL,10,FOther astronomers have accused him of
OL,11,Fmaking claims with little evidence.
OL,12,FSome have criticised his habit of
OL,13,Fskipping the peer review process and
OL,14,Fbringing claims directly to the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FSteve Desch, an Arizona State
OL,7,FUniversity astrophysicist who has
OL,8,Fchallenged some of Loeb's theories,
OL,9,Fsaid Loeb uses flawed methods to reach
OL,10,Fwild conclusions about alien life,
OL,11,Fwhile shunning a more established
OL,12,Fbranch of science searching for life
OL,13,Fbeyond Earth.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FLoeb's role on the White House panel
OL,7,Fcasts doubt on the entire endeavour,
OL,8,FDesch said.
OL,10,F"I don't know what's going to come of
OL,11,Fthis, but we're not going to get any
OL,12,Fcloser to answering these questions
OL,13,Fwith him in charge," Desch said.
OL,15,FSean Kirkpatrick, a physicist who
OL,16,Fpreviously investigated UAP at the
OL,17,FPentagon's All-domain Anomaly
OL,18,FResolution Office, said Loeb is "not
OL,19,Fviewed favourably" in the scientific
OL,20,Fcommunity and lacks national security
OL,21,Fexperience.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@TO]zD@aOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782886685
OL,3,CWhite House picks controversial alien
OL,4,Ctheorist to lead UFO council
OL,6,FHe said the makeup of Loeb's team
OL,7,Fsuggests the White House is more
OL,8,Finterested in fringe theories than
OL,9,Fhard science.
OL,11,FThe White House did not respond to a
OL,12,Frequest for comment about the
OL,13,Fcriticism.
OL,15,FLoeb, meanwhile, said he aims to
OL,16,Ffollow the science without distraction.
OL,18,F"Let's keep our eyes on the orbs," he
OL,19,Fsaid, "not the social media."
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@bO]{D@GOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
